data.name: title
data.description: Title the contact holds within their company

data.name: id
data.description: ID of the contact to be updated

data.name: from
data.description: From_address from which the email campaign will be sent

data.name: from_label
data.description: The form label for the email campaign

data.name: message
data.value: Please attend Joe's Party this Summer! Details are here!

data.name: postal_address
data.description: Postal address of the sender. Required by law.

data.name: reply_to
data.description: The reply_to email address in the email campaign

data.name: unsubscribe_message
data.description: The unsubscribe message for the email campaign. Required by law.
data.value: No longer wish to receive these emails? Click here.

data.name: email_id
data.description: Email ID for the email to be launched

data.name: lists
data.description: Array of list IDs to send the email to. Maximum 50 list IDs allowed.

data.name: scheduled_at
data.description: Optional date flag specifying when to send the email

description: VerticalResponse helps users create and send great email campaigns. We make contact and list management easy, allowing users to create contacts, group them into meaningful lists, and use these lists to send targeted email campaigns. VerticalResponse provides REST APIs to manage contacts, lists, messages and custom fields. Developers can integrate VerticalResponse's email and social marketing functionality into their applications to provide their customers with new and interesting ways to create and manage marketing campaigns.
name: v1
